      "comment": "NITRO NED (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Aston Crema (17.54) in a Grade 6. Has the pace to be prominent. Sure to be about the mark. VIVID LOVE (6) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when third (17.84) in a Grade 5/6 at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. JUST MUST (3) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing second (17.53) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 297m. Will give a great sight again. WIZARD'S NOVA (1) can sneak into the finish.",
